<br>
  Another technique to &quot;Box&quot; involves the Main Tank only.  If all the melee are attacking from the Bad Guy's backside, and the Bad Guy is getting pushed too far one way, the Main Tank simply flips around to the other side of the Bad Guy, and all the melee flip as well, continuing to attack the backside.  This will effectively push the Baddie in the opposite direction.<br>
